= Revision history for jekyll-rendering

== 0.0.9 []

* Include backtrace in render_error.
* Use "lazy" OpenStruct for Erb.

== 0.0.8 [2012-05-22]

* Added support for Erubis. (Used by default if available.)
* Work around encoding issues on Ruby 1.9.

== 0.0.7 [2011-03-31]

* Include ERB::Util in Jekyll::Rendering::Erb::Helpers.

== 0.0.6 [2011-03-09]

* Defined Jekyll::Rendering::ERB_OPTIONS to allow
  adjusting behaviour of ERB.new.

== 0.0.5 [2010-10-29]

* Refactored include_file.
  * Accept hash of local assigns instead of binding.
  * Denote inclusion from current directory by './'.

== 0.0.4 [2010-10-01]

* Allow inclusion of files from *current* directory.

== 0.0.3 [2010-09-29]

* Fixed nested layouts.

== 0.0.2 [2010-07-01]

* Refactoring and documentation.
	* Introduced Jekyll::Engine::Erb::Helpers module
	* Provide aliases to original methods
* Credits.

== 0.0.1 [2010-06-30]

* Birthday :-)
